Program_Title: Rep. Jean Schmidt (R-OH) Speaks in Favor of No Taxpayer Funding for Abortion Act.wmv

Headlines: Rep. Jean Schmidt (R-OH) discusses the history of the right-to-life movement, all the way back to the woman of the suffrage movement, including Susan B. Anthony. Rep. Schmidt gives a listen that all Americans should know, as the original feminists were pro-life! Rep. Schmidt has been a hero for the pro-life movement in Congress since her election.
